40__RCSID("$NetBSD: gelf_symshndx.c,v 1.3 2016/02/20 02:43:42 christos Exp $");
41ELFTC_VCSID("Id: gelf_symshndx.c 3174 2015-03-27 17:13:41Z emaste ");

43GElf_Sym *
44gelf_getsymshndx(Elf_Data *d, Elf_Data *id, int ndx, GElf_Sym *dst,
45 Elf32_Word *shindex)
46{
47 int ec;
48 Elf *e;
49 size_t msz;
50 Elf_Scn *scn;
51 uint32_t sh_type;
52 struct _Libelf_Data *ld, *lid;
53
54 ld = (struct _Libelf_Data *) d;
55 lid = (struct _Libelf_Data *) id;
56
57 if (gelf_getsym(d, ndx, dst) == 0)
58 return (NULL);
59
60 if (lid == NULL || (scn = lid->d_scn) == NULL ||
61 (e = scn->s_elf) == NULL || (e != ld->d_scn->s_elf) ||
62 shindex == NULL) {
63 LIBELF_SET_ERROR(ARGUMENT, 0);
64 return (NULL);
65 }
66
67 ec = e->e_class;
68 assert(ec == ELFCLASS32 || ec == ELFCLASS64);
69
70 if (ec == ELFCLASS32)
71 sh_type = scn->s_shdr.s_shdr32.sh_type;
72 else
73 sh_type = scn->s_shdr.s_shdr64.sh_type;
74
75 if (_libelf_xlate_shtype(sh_type) != ELF_T_WORD ||
76 id->d_type != ELF_T_WORD) {
77 LIBELF_SET_ERROR(ARGUMENT, 0);
78 return (NULL);
79 }
80
81 msz = _libelf_msize(ELF_T_WORD, ec, e->e_version);
82
83 assert(msz > 0);
84 assert(ndx >= 0);
85
86 if (msz * (size_t) ndx >= id->d_size) {
87 LIBELF_SET_ERROR(ARGUMENT, 0);
88 return (NULL);
89 }
90
91 *shindex = ((Elf32_Word *) id->d_buf)[ndx];
92
93 return (dst);
94}
95
96int
97gelf_update_symshndx(Elf_Data *d, Elf_Data *id, int ndx, GElf_Sym *gs,
98 Elf32_Word xindex)
99{
100 int ec;
101 Elf *e;
102 size_t msz;
103 Elf_Scn *scn;
104 uint32_t sh_type;
105 struct _Libelf_Data *ld, *lid;
106
107 ld = (struct _Libelf_Data *) d;
108 lid = (struct _Libelf_Data *) id;
109
110 if (gelf_update_sym(d, ndx, gs) == 0)
111 return (0);
112
113 if (lid == NULL || (scn = lid->d_scn) == NULL ||
114 (e = scn->s_elf) == NULL || (e != ld->d_scn->s_elf)) {
115 LIBELF_SET_ERROR(ARGUMENT, 0);
116 return (0);
117 }
118
119 ec = e->e_class;
120 assert(ec == ELFCLASS32 || ec == ELFCLASS64);
121
122 if (ec == ELFCLASS32)
123 sh_type = scn->s_shdr.s_shdr32.sh_type;
124 else
125 sh_type = scn->s_shdr.s_shdr64.sh_type;
126
127 if (_libelf_xlate_shtype(sh_type) != ELF_T_WORD ||
128 d->d_type != ELF_T_WORD) {
129 LIBELF_SET_ERROR(ARGUMENT, 0);
130 return (0);
131 }
132
133 msz = _libelf_msize(ELF_T_WORD, ec, e->e_version);
134
135 assert(msz > 0);
136 assert(ndx >= 0);
137
138 if (msz * (size_t) ndx >= id->d_size) {
139 LIBELF_SET_ERROR(ARGUMENT, 0);
140 return (0);
141 }
142
143 *(((Elf32_Word *) id->d_buf) + ndx) = xindex;
144
145 return (1);
146}
